    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Lab Cats》是一款强调合作与协调的解谜平台游戏，玩家需要无缝地协同作战。在这场合作冒险中，玩家将操控两只猫咪，试图逃离充满障碍的复杂实验室，这些障碍只能通过团队合作来克服。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335050/extras/188620c9e02fedde6dec0ad2d6c99853.poster.avif?t=1768293642\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335050/extras/188620c9e02fedde6dec0ad2d6c99853.webm?t=1768293642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335050/extras/188620c9e02fedde6dec0ad2d6c99853.mp4?t=1768293642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335050/extras/25698d17f3aa84b7b80f3c5e6546a839.webp?t=1768293642\" width=600 height=27 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个以猫作为实验对象的实验室中，一位心生不满的科学家决定挺身而出。为了逃离这个可怕的地方，他释放了两只勇敢的猫，并将一项任务托付给它们：逃出实验室，并从外面的世界带回援助。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335050/extras/21fd525ff9e5bbbcbf369e5aa0f904de.poster.avif?t=1768293642\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335050/extras/21fd525ff9e5bbbcbf369e5aa0f904de.webm?t=1768293642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335050/extras/21fd525ff9e5bbbcbf369e5aa0f904de.mp4?t=1768293642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335050/extras/3385b7d6fdc7d5690d874aa386677787.webp?t=1768293642\" width=600 height=27 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >猫咪们利用它们的特殊项圈，根据移动来启动或关闭按钮。这项创新的机制要求玩家谨慎规划移动，并进行策略性的团队合作来解决难题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335050/extras/f1c5694fb3cabeda6eea6aac1ffc2127.poster.avif?t=1768293642\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335050/extras/f1c5694fb3cabeda6eea6aac1ffc2127.webm?t=1768293642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335050/extras/f1c5694fb3cabeda6eea6aac1ffc2127.mp4?t=1768293642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家必须运用这些机制，展现个人技巧与团队合作的能力！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335050/extras/f319cd6cc45f8ec04c65b174057db014.poster.avif?t=1768293642\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335050/extras/f319cd6cc45f8ec04c65b174057db014.webm?t=1768293642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335050/extras/f319cd6cc45f8ec04c65b174057db014.mp4?t=1768293642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
